---
// Footer.astro - Minimalist & Strategic
---

<footer class="border-t border-gray-100 py-20 mt-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-end">
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <a href="/" class="text-xl font-black tracking-tighter hover:text-gray-400 transition-colors">
                    WANBE<span class="text-gray-300">.</span>
                </a>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed max-w-xs italic font-serif">
                    Building a healthy and meaningful living space. <br/>
                    <a href="/about" class="text-black font-bold not-italic hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-gray-300 transition-all">
                        Learn Our Philosophy →
                    </a>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:items-end gap-4">
                <div class="flex gap-6 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-black text-gray-400">
                    <a href="https://id.pinterest.com/wanbe_/" class="hover:text-black transition-colors">Pinterest</a>
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/wanbe777_/" class="hover:text-black transition-colors">Instagram</a>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">
                    &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Wanbe. All rights reserved.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</footer>